#10101
shopkeeper Masuin~
shopkeeper Masuin~
The shopkeeper Masuin stands here to sell you all your last minute needs.
~
~
2051 0 0 S
0 0 -300 32000d1+0 0d0+0
0 0
112 112 0
#10102
attendant Chrav~
the attendant~
Chrav the attendant is sitting behind a counter here to register you.
~
~
3 0 0 S
0 0 0 32700d1+0 0d0+0
0 0
112 112 0
> speech_prog p register~
if isfollow($n)
mpecho _lbl The attendant says 'Hmm, seems that you're following someone else, the leader will have to check you in.'
else
'Ah, yes, your name is $n, I'll be happy to write you down here...
mpecho The attendant scribbles something or another down on a pad of paper.
'Allright, now I will show you in.
mpopenpassage 10104 10105 0
mpecho The attendant unlocks a door north.
mpforce 0.$n n
mpclosepassage 10104 0
endif
~
|
