#0


#ROOMS
#10101
The Arena entryway~
You are standing in the entrance hall of the Arena.  Here, a group of players,
or just one player if they are truely brave, may take on a task to test many
qualities of their own, and in passing recieve great rewards.  To the east is
a built-in inn, and to the west is a shop, both put here for battle-preparation
for the adventurers.  To the north is a door.  Going through it will mean you
are ready to face the tasks at hand.  Once you go through that door, there is
no coming out until you have chosen and completed a task, that or the OTHER way
out, but most don't look forward to that.
~
~
0 8 0 3
D0
~
~
0 -1 10104
D6
~
~
0 -1 10102
D7
~
~
0 -1 10103
M 10101 2 2 !
S
#10102
Arena Inn~
This is a small room, made so because it's only to serve a simple purpose, and
that is to rest before battle.  Though it may be small it is nonetheless
extravegant, 
~
~
0 8 0 0
D9
~
~
0 -1 10101
M 10101 3 1 I
S
#10103
Arena Store~
This is the Arena Store.  A simple place to buy some last minute general goods,
like food and water especially, also things that may or may not be of importance
depending upon what you choose to accomplish here.  The best thing to do is be
at max health and everything when venturing into one of the tasks, for there's
no telling what will come despite how strong you think you are.
~
~
0 8 0 0
D8
~
~
0 -1 10101
M 10101 1 1 $
S
#10104
Entering the Arena~
Welcome to the Arena.  No point in turning back now, so get ready to partcipate
in an event of your own choosing for prizes and entertainment or spectators.
Please sign in by saying "register" and the attendant will show you through.
Note that if you are part of a group, the leader must sign in, that or
disband the group.
~
~
0 12 0 0
M 10101 2 1 !
> act_prog p arrives from the south.~
if isfollow($n)
else
if mobinworld(10103) == 0
and mobinworld(10104) == 0
and mobinworld(10105) == 0
mpopenpassage 10105 10106 3
endif
endif
~
|
S
#10105
Choosing your fate~
You are standing in a room with an a multiple of doors.  The idea now is
simple, you get to choose your own fate.  Once you have gone through you'll
have to figure out what you're supposed to do in most cases, then do it while
attempting to come back out alive and without too many things to tell stories
about at the academy the second time around.
~
~
0 12 0 0
M 10102 10 5 o
> act_prog p arrives from the west.~
if isfollow($n)
or mortcount(10200) > 0
else
The attendant arrives from the south.
mpecho _lbl The attendant says 'Great job $n, you've done splendidly.  Allow me the honor of showing you to where you can collect your prize.'
mpopenpassage 10105 10200 4
mpecho The attendant reveals a staircase going upstairs.
mpechoat $n You decide to go up there to collect your prize.
mpforce 0.$n u
mpclosepassage 10105 4
mpecho The attendant leaves south.
endif
~
> act_prog p arrives from the west.~
if isfollow($n)
mpopenpassage 10105 10106 3
mpclosepassage 10106 1
endif
~
|
S
#10106
The Arena~
You are in the open area of the Arena, with large rows of seats all around you
reaching high up into the sky, filled with people.  The world here is full of
their chatter, and find it difficult to focus your mind.  Best that you can
tell, you are at the east side of the arena.
~
~
