> act_prog p arrives from the east.~
if isfollow($n)
else
mpat 10161 mpmload 10103
mpat 10139 mpmload 10103
mpat 10117 mpmload 10105
mpat 10120 mpmload 10104
mpat 10143 mpmload 10104
mpat 10123 mpmload 10105
mpecho You hear the attendant announce 'Attention spectators of this great arena, we have today for you an even to behold.  Watch now as the adventures attempt to rid the area of the creatures in combat.
mpclosepassage 10105 3
mpclosepassage 10106 1
endif
~
