#10107
The Arena~
You stand further north on the east side of the arena.  It all looks alike,
and you wonder if this is where you came in from, or was it north, or maybe it
had been southeast.  It doesn't matter, none of them have an open passage, your
predicament seems to be that of kill or be killed.  You can sense your enemy
somewhere about you, hear it's footsteps, it's breathing.  You look to the
crowd but they give no answer, their faces unrevealing from this far to offer
any help.  They've probably betted for the other side anyways.
~
~
