#10108
The Arena~
As far as you can tell, you are on the eastern side of the arena, though that's
not exactly an easy guess since it's been made to look similar on every side,
probably for the added element of confusion to both you and your enemy.
Seats cover the mass of the walls in their slopes, filled with peoples without
features to you roaring in some kind of cheerful or booing noise at your
every movement.
~
~
