#10139
The Arena~
East wasn't it?  That you came from?  You realize yourself breathing pretty
heavily, wondering how long until you get out of here and claim your prizes.
The sun is still out in the sky, and the light makes it not overly difficult
to sense youe enemy's presence about you and to see it's form moving around in
the close distance.
~
It's very dark.  The undistinguishable features of the crowd are now even more,
you can see just hundreds of forms all around you still watching in awe as you
move about and attack.  The moon light gives little help, you can't see anyone
around here, though it's presence you can feel, and hear.
~
